title: Clinton vs Obama: Democratic Primary Vote, New Hampshire, 2008
name: Clinton vs Obama: Democratic Primary Vote, New Hampshire, 2008
description: Spatial comparison of votes for Clinton and Obama in the New Hampshire primary.      Primary votes data is based on the Concord Monitor website when more than 95% precinct results were announced:      http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/files/elections/2008/by_state/NH_Page_0108.html?SITE=NHCONELN&SECTION=POLITICS      The cities/towns were geocoded based on NH Secretary of State website for City/Town Clerks office locations (http://www.sos.nh.gov/clerks.htm).
